<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 12:24:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>线粒体 Ca2+ 流出控制跨物种的神经元代谢和长期记忆</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mitochondrial-ca2-efflux-controls-neuronal-metabolism-and-long-term-memory-across-species</link><description>线粒体钙调节神经元代谢和记忆。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mitochondrial-ca2-efflux-controls-neuronal-metabolism-and-long-term-memory-across-species.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 12:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mitochondrial-ca2-efflux-controls-neuronal-metabolism-and-long-term-memory-across-species</guid></item><item><title>加速和简化微生物工艺开发</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/accelerating-and-streamlining-microbial-process-development</link><description>CDMO Fujifilm Biotechnologies 推出了 ShunzymeX 精密纯化技术，旨在简化复杂生物制剂的下游加工。该技术将于本周在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/accelerating-and-streamlining-microbial-process-development.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 12:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/accelerating-and-streamlining-microbial-process-development</guid></item><item><title>退化的 Tanycytes 会破坏 Tau 蛋白的去除，从而影响阿尔茨海默病的进展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/degenerating-tanycytes-disrupt-tau-removal-shaping-alzheimers-progression</link><description>作者写道：“Tanycytes 的细胞体排列在第三脑室的壁和底板上，并延伸出长而细的过程，终止于接触这些有孔毛细血管的‘端脚’，”充当脑脊液和血液之间的穿梭机。这项新研究表明，它们还充当一种分子“出口坡道”，将 tau 蛋白从脑脊液中移出并进入血液进行处理。当这些细胞变得支离破碎时，清除系统就会动摇。本应被运走的 Tau 蛋白却徘徊不去——就像主要出口匝道关闭时交通拥堵一样——导致有毒蛋白质种类积累。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/degenerating-tanycytes-disrupt-tau-removal-shaping-alzheimers-progression.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 11:54:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/degenerating-tanycytes-disrupt-tau-removal-shaping-alzheimers-progression</guid></item><item><title>一个富裕的家庭能改变致命脑部疾病的病程吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-a-wealthy-family-change-the-course-of-a-deadly-brain-disease</link><description>一个富裕家庭与自己的疾病作斗争，推动了对一种很少被研究的大脑蛋白质颗粒体蛋白前体的研究。它能刺激新的痴呆症治疗吗？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-a-wealthy-family-change-the-course-of-a-deadly-brain-disease.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 11:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-a-wealthy-family-change-the-course-of-a-deadly-brain-disease</guid></item><item><title>RAB3GAP2 是骨骼肌内皮细胞增殖的调节剂，与毛细血管与纤维的比率相关</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/rab3gap2-is-a-regulator-of-skeletal-muscle-endothelial-cell-proliferation-and-associated-with-capillary-to-fiber-ratio</link><description>斯特罗姆等人。识别 rs115660502 变体&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/rab3gap2-is-a-regulator-of-skeletal-muscle-endothelial-cell-proliferation-and-associated-with-capillary-to-fiber-ratio2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 11:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/rab3gap2-is-a-regulator-of-skeletal-muscle-endothelial-cell-proliferation-and-associated-with-capillary-to-fiber-ratio</guid></item><item><title>阿拉曼定受体 MrgD 表达在伴有转移性疾病的透明细胞肾细胞癌中的预后和治疗意义</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/prognostic-and-therapeutic-implications-of-alamandine-receptor-mrgd-expression-in-clear-cell-renal-cell-carcinoma-with-development-of-metastatic-disease</link><description>尽管晚期透明细胞肾细胞癌（ccRCC）的治疗取得了进展，但用于预后和治疗反应预测的可靠生物标志物仍然难以捉摸。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/prognostic-and-therapeutic-implications-of-alamandine-receptor-mrgd-expression-in-clear-cell-renal-cell-carcinoma-with-development-of-metastatic-disease2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 11:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/prognostic-and-therapeutic-implications-of-alamandine-receptor-mrgd-expression-in-clear-cell-renal-cell-carcinoma-with-development-of-metastatic-disease</guid></item><item><title>像太阳这样的恒星可能会在生命中保持相同的旋转模式，这与 45 年的理论预测相反</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/stars-like-our-sun-may-maintain-the-same-rotation-pattern-for-life-contrary-to-45-years-of-theoretical-predictions</link><description>日本名古屋大学的研究人员对恒星内部进行了最详细的模拟，并反驳了科学家们 45 年来一直相信的理论：恒星随着年龄的增长而改变其旋转模式，老年恒星中的极点旋转速度比赤道旋转速度更快。科学家现在发现这种转变可能不会发生。恒星在其一生中都保持着太阳式的自转，在赤道快速旋转，在两极缓慢旋转。研究结果发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/stars-like-our-sun-may-maintain-the-same-rotation-pattern-for-life-contrary-to-45-years-of-theoretical-predictions.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 10:54:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/stars-like-our-sun-may-maintain-the-same-rotation-pattern-for-life-contrary-to-45-years-of-theoretical-predictions</guid></item><item><title>液态金属瞳孔有助于人造眼适应突然的光线变化</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/liquid-metal-pupil-helps-an-artificial-eye-adapt-to-sudden-light-changes</link><description>计算机视觉技术是人工智能 (AI) 支持的系统，可以捕获、分析和解释从现实世界环境中捕获的视觉数据。虽然这些系统现在被广泛使用，但其中许多系统在某些照明条件下以及捕获场景中的光线突然变化时表现不佳。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/liquid-metal-pupil-helps-an-artificial-eye-adapt-to-sudden-light-changes2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 10:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/liquid-metal-pupil-helps-an-artificial-eye-adapt-to-sudden-light-changes</guid></item><item><title>中子星内部有什么？新模型可以增强引力波“潮汐”线索</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/whats-inside-neutron-stars-new-model-could-sharpen-gravitational-wave-tide-clues</link><description>中子星拥有宇宙中一些最极端的环境：它们的密度飙升至原子核的几倍，并且它们拥有已知物体中最强的引力场，仅次于黑洞。中子星于 20 世纪 60 年代首次被观测到，但其大部分内部成分仍然未知。科学家们开始将双中子星螺旋（相互绕轨道运行的中子星对）发射的引力波视为有关其内部信息的可能来源。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/whats-inside-neutron-stars-new-model-could-sharpen-gravitational-wave-tide-clues.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 10:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/whats-inside-neutron-stars-new-model-could-sharpen-gravitational-wave-tide-clues</guid></item><item><title>研究人员通过组合多个光信号来检测复杂的情绪</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/researchers-detect-complex-emotions-by-combining-multiple-optical-signals</link><description>研究人员通过将基于纤维的生理信号与面部热图像相结合，开发出了一种识别人类情绪的新方法。便携式情绪识别系统最终可用于支持家庭心理健康监测、提高驾驶员安全并使技术对人类情绪更加敏感。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-detect-complex-emotions-by-combining-multiple-optical-signals.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 10:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/researchers-detect-complex-emotions-by-combining-multiple-optical-signals</guid></item></channel></rss>